Package jade.gen

Interface Summary
Gen An inteface used for generating random maps on a jade world.
 

Class Summary
BSP This implementation of Gen uses a binary space partition tree
Cellular This implementation of Gen uses cellular automata to generate interesting cave level.
Gen.GenFactory Used for retrieving varius singleton instances of Gen implementing classes.
Town This implementation of Gen takes a simple wilderness and adds a few buildings.
Traditional This implementation of Gen generates traditional looking dungeons.
Wilderness This implemenatation of Gen generates a simple wilderness.
